Class ShipContainer

java.lang.Object
ShipContainer
Direct Known Subclasses:
ManualContentList, ShippingContainerRFID
public abstract class ShipContainer
extends java.lang.Object
The ShipContainer class is an abstract base class representing a common interface for managing container contents and tracking the container's ID.
